raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
if Story.has_flag(\"NinasPanties\"):
	Player: Hey!
	Player: I got it!
	Jason: You mad man
	Jason: You got Nina's panties!?
	Player: I did
	Player: img: other/9
	Jason: Fucking mad man
	Jason: No one's gonna believe you tbh lmao
	Jason: Got any more proof?
	Player: I have a pic of her wearing them and text confirming it 😆
	Jason: That should do it
	Jason: Bring them with you, we'll go after class
	Jason: Don't lose them, that's probably the rarest pair of panties you'll ever find lmao
	Player: I'm guarding them with my life!
	Jason: 😂
	Jason: Anyway, glad you managed
	do social_post(\"nina_gangbang\")
else:
	Jason: Yo dude!
	Jason: Pick brown or yellow
	- Brown? [#brownheart]
		Player: Brown?
		Jason: img: jason/4
	- Yellow?? [#yellowheart]
		Player: Yellow??
		Jason: img: jason/3
	Jason: You got it
	Player: Wait you have 2?
	Jason: Goldfish memory huh?
	Jason: Of course I got 2, don't you remember 😂
	Player: How could I forget...
	Jason: 😆
	Jason: Called in some favors from the ladies
	Jason: They actually can't wait to meet you
	Player: Wait what?
	Player: What did you do 😅
	Jason: Not much
	Jason: Just told them that you have a bigger dick than me
	Player: 😂
	Jason: 😜
	Jason: Anyway, no friend like me chief 😉
	Jason: I expect you to take this gift all the way
	Player: Damn, I will bro!
	Player: Thanks!
	Jason: All good broski
Jason: We'll meet up after class and sign up together
Player: Sounds like a plan!
Player: I don't know much about the frat house though
Jason: That's okay, we'll get the gist of it on the weekend I hear
Jason: Once we're in, we'll get all the deets
Player: Sounds good
Jason: Gotta do this bullshit paperwork now
Jason: Alright catch you later, clubbies... 
Jason: Ehh... club mem... 
Jason: Club fam?
Jason: Later chief
Player: Later 😁
=> END"
